98) 25 周年纪念再版，</a>以纪念<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/national-album-day-2023-to-pay-homage-1990s-albums-3413258">国家专辑日，</a>随后宣布了这一消息。</p><p> Fatboy Slim 将于 11 月 10 日至 13 日举行的第二届<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-announces-line-up-for-2023-all-back-to-minehead-festival-3428309">All Back to Minehead Festival</a>上亮相。您可以<a href="https://www.butlins.com/bigweekenders/weekends/fatboy-slim-presents-all-back-to-minehead/minehead-101123" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到该活动的所有剩余门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-announces-2023-uk-tour-yall-are-the-music-were-just-the-djs-3311760">这位 DJ 还于三月份开始了他的“Y&#39;all Are The Music, We&#39;re Just The DJ”英国巡演，最近</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fatboy-slim-perform-on-worlds-biggest-holographic-stage-3518871">Fatboy Slim（或者更确切地说，他的全息肖像）在伦敦亚历山德拉宫进行了一场惊喜表演</a>。后来，他在北爱尔兰德里的演出中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-invites-derry-girls-cast-on-stage-in-derry-3519082">邀请了<em>德里女孩 (Derry Girls)</em>演员作为惊喜嘉宾</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-confirms-2024-loves-summer-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3525849">Fatboy Slim 确认 2024 年“Loves Summer”英国和爱尔兰巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
